title: 3 BR Cozy 55+ Living Calling Your Name at The Legends of Woodbury!
map_address: 570 Settlers Ridge Parkway near Hudson Rd
posting_body: ['This luxurious community offers one, two and three bedroom apartment homes, as well spacious different floor plans for each living arrangement.', 'The Legends of Woodbury, placed conveniently by many parks, dining and shopping spots, has everything that you are looking for in 55+ living.', 'We wanted to spoil our residents, so we decided to get each apartment home washers and dryers, a kitchen breakfast bar and island, a private balcony, and large walk-in closets!', 'The community of the Legends of Woodbury has everything you want in a 55+ living complex, and more!', 'We provide our residents with a spacious theater room, a cards and crafts room, a cozy community area with a fireplace, a fitness center and underground heated parking.', 'Our community is pet friendly and even has an outdoor dog run!', 'If you have any questions about your pet joining you in your home, please call our professional on-site management team.', 'Reserve your 55+ living apartment home today at the Legends of Woodbury!', 'NOTE: Office Hours - By Appointment Only.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Professional On-Site Management Team', '- Card & Crafts Room', '- Full-Size Washer & Dryer', 'In EVERY Home!', '- Landscaped Outdoor Seating Area', '- Open & Spacious Floor Plans', '- Theater Room', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Woodbury is a community for active seniors that participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'At least one household member must be at least 55 years of age.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Woodbury', '570 Settlers Ridge Parkway', 'Woodbury, MN, 55129', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'LZ0g59Fxn']
